21,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T00:16:54.000Z","msg":"Push<br />\n利申: 見到依家得31架參加表示..."},{"pid":"1fd570d115423c4d95472c98d93f25f40d3cd749","tid":1762530,"uid":326321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T00:22:57.000Z","msg":"其實十二月七號仲有兩個有意義嘅活動，大家可以去嫁！<br />\n<br />\n12月7日 ( 六 )：<br />\n<br />\n#7Dec #荃灣 #送暖行動<br />\n葵荃送暖行動3.0<br />\n時間 : 09 : 30 - 12 : 30<br />\n地點 : 荃灣公園入口<br />\n活動內容:為老友記量血壓<br />\n*如手足有任何疑問和提議，歡迎利用 @hkpplmobot 查詢<br />\nLink : <a href=\"https://t.me/hkpplmo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkpplmo&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbY5bpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=f6afde1c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkpplmo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#7Dec #中環 #集會 #姐姐都是手足<br />\n🆕聲援被逐印傭作家集會<br />\n時間：15:00 - 17:00<br />\n地點：中環愛丁堡廣場<br />\n🌟不反對通知書申請中<br />\nChannel： @standwithyuli  <br />\n公海： @thankyouyuli"},{"pid":"59c202b43beb7b7a5d867484233a2d2dfa57e1d5","tid":1762530,"uid":92247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T03:35:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ef14f2bb44c92677e63e24ddbfc950423311593","tid":1762530,"uid":92247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T08:58:09.000Z","msg":"Pishhhhh"},{"pid":"931163b28c7d8245f926b2436f968abb8bedc6c8","tid":1762530,"uid":92247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T09:05:26.000Z","msg":"最後一推。冇力了"},{"pid":"14206f7b1878696409a5f99de10b3ca33f596c0b","tid":1762530,"uid":77302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T09:08:59.000Z","msg":"push!"},{"pid":"591bea29cc70b246751bd2649d0e1215fabf4d8f","tid":1762530,"uid":77302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T09:09:26.000Z","msg":"行動post無人理？"},{"pid":"c7be1828c